cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR 

The paper deals with the problem of grounding textual phrases in images, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method involves using weak supervision and end-to-end learning, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves retrieval and alignment of captions, which are tasks related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
